My VIM files
============

Installation
------------

    # Get the files into your home drive
    git clone https://github.com/daveroberts/vimfiles.git ~/.vim/

    # make a symbolic link from/to .vimrc
    ln -sf ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc

    # Packages controlled by Vundle; Install it
    git clone https://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git ~/.vim/bundle/vundle/

    # I use droid fonts; To install on Ubuntu
    sudo apt-get install fonts-droid

    # Install packages
    start gvim
    run command :BundleInstall by typing ;BundleInstall<Enter>

Adding libraries
----------------

    # To install a new plugin, add it to the .vimrc file and rebundle
